# Static site (canonical)

- **Work at repo root** — HTML pages, `css/main.css`, `js/*.js`, images, fonts.
- No Astro, no build step.
- Deploy: GitHub Actions uploads the repo root to Pages on push to `main`.
- Keep root-relative asset paths (`/css/`, `/images/`, `/js/`).
- Research pages: `research/<slug>/index.html`.
- Nav scroll-spy lives in `js/nav.js`; scroll cue in `js/scroll-cue.js`.
